These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Job: analyst, entrepreneur, bartender, dressmaker
Flower: poppy, zinnia, balloon-flower, orchid
1. Job:analyst is on the right of Flower:balloon-flower##1
2. Flower:orchid is on the far left##1
3. Flower:balloon-flower is between Flower:zinnia and Job:entrepreneur##2
4. Job:dressmaker is on the far left##1
5. Job:bartender is between Job:entrepreneur and Job:analyst##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Job   | dressmaker         | entrepreneur   | bartender | analyst       |
| Flower      | orchid | poppy | balloon-flower   | zinnia |

