.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
House: farmhouse, craftsman, wooden, futuristic
Color: blood-red, light-blue, turquise, grey
1. Color:grey is between House:wooden and Color:light-blue##2
2. House:futuristic is on the far right##1
3. Color:turquise is on the right of Color:blood-red##1
4. House:farmhouse is on the left of Color:blood-red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| House         | craftsman | farmhouse | wooden | futuristic |
| Color   | light-blue    | grey   | blood-red | turquise       |

