.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
Sport: surfing, weightlifting, golf, baseball
Transport: bike, tram, train, van
1. Transport:train is on the right of Sport:baseball##1
2. Transport:train is between Transport:tram and Sport:weightlifting##2
3. Transport:tram is on the far left##1
4. Transport:van is on the left of Sport:golf##1
5. Sport:weightlifting == Transport:van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Sport          | baseball    | surfing | weightlifting   | golf  |
| Transport   | tram | train   | van | bike |

